23#include "mpfr-impl.h"
24
25const char *
26mpfr_print_rnd_mode (mpfr_rnd_t rnd_mode)
27{
28 /* If we forget to update this function after a new rounding mode
29 is added, this will be detected by the following assertion. */
30 MPFR_STAT_STATIC_ASSERT (MPFR_RND_MAX == MPFR_RNDF + 1);
31 switch (rnd_mode)
32 {
33 case MPFR_RNDD:
34 return "MPFR_RNDD";
35 case MPFR_RNDU:
36 return "MPFR_RNDU";
37 case MPFR_RNDN:
38 return "MPFR_RNDN";
39 case MPFR_RNDZ:
40 return "MPFR_RNDZ";
41 case MPFR_RNDA:
42 return "MPFR_RNDA";
43 case MPFR_RNDF:
44 return "MPFR_RNDF";
45 default:
46 return (const char*) 0;
47 }
48}
